{"tid":1156160,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"柯尿嗰陣痾到開叉嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T13:25:26.000Z","uid":96097,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c09282a7e30960c69e2d31d37077f341e08098","tid":1156160,"uid":96097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"屌那星 都係呢1-2年嘅事 條巨龍間唔中痾到開叉 <br />\n<br />\n 清醒嗰陣都可以用左手嘅食指控制到佢<br />\n<br />\n但唔清醒嗰陣 半夜柯尿/一朝早起身痾尿（仲有扯緊嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）開叉開到過90度都有 實痾到出晒界<br />\n<br />\n試過返工嗰陣痾 射到對鞋 好在冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有同樣情況？係咪要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩解決方法？淨係諗住坐係度痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bc04164b88b3e47187e52d30e499aa8aa294c4","tid":1156160,"uid":30404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"咪打咁多飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3005990e1484762716e50b7ad87a9c8738385e3","tid":1156160,"uid":72475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"腎有時"},{"pid":"471b889f2257a405c40d029a45a3fdbfffc892af","tid":1156160,"uid":15624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:28:07.000Z","msg":"你啲鳩毛撥開先屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109c5b971568d36376cec0e9fe69c7603e00739b","tid":1156160,"uid":29166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"係咪打得太多丁"},{"pid":"9365f03bca50207cdd95f9c7a2c479b6a2c119bf","tid":1156160,"uid":96097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4bc04164b88b3e47187e52d30e499aa8aa294c4","tid":1156160,"uid":30404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:19:57.000Z","m